ECS Hub Centric Ring Adapter Set - 74.1mm Wheels to 72.56mm Hub
   ...
short-description: These hub centric rings are required when fitting 74.1mm hub-bore wheels to any other 72.56mm BMW 5-lug chassis. Some BMWs, such as the E39, uses a larger center bore on the wheel (74.1mm) but most other BMWs have a 72.5mm lip on the hub. That little difference will cause the wheel to not fully seat itself on the hub, even when fully torqued down. These centering rings fill that gap and allow the wheel to rest properly on the hub.
